      },
      {
        "step_no": 2,
        "text": "Combine tuna and dressing: in a medium bowl, flake the drained tuna with a fork, add mayonnaise, lime juice, olive oil, ground cumin (if using), salt and pepper, then stir until evenly coated and slightly chunky.",
