      },
      {
        "step_no": 3,
        "text": "Fold in fresh mix-ins: add the diced tomato, red onion, cilantro and minced jalapeño to the tuna mixture and gently fold to combine; taste and adjust seasoning with more salt, lime or hot sauce as desired.",
        "time_min": 3
      },
      {
        "step_no": 4,
        "text": "Assemble tostadas: place a layer of shredded cabbage or lettuce on each tostada to protect from sogginess, divide the tuna mixture evenly among the tostadas, then top with diced avocado and an extra sprinkle of cilantro and black pepper.",
